metadata.description:
Faylen is an elf who lives in the future age. She was born from one of elven nobility. What she learned from childhood times is the fact that nobility isn't great at all. For her, they are only people who are greedy for wealth. Because of that, she renounced her peerage and became a rogue. Moving in the shadows to seize properties of the nobles, and then share what she got to lowly people.

2160x2160 / MP4 / 30 FPS / 10 sec / RaptorVz, 2021
metadata.name: Faylen #1/20
